Privacy Policy for Watch Face Application
Effective Date:
July 2, 2024
Introduction
We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our watch face application.
Information Collection and Use
No Data Collection:
The Watch Face Application does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data from your device.
Use of Device Information:
The application uses information such as step count and heart rate directly from your device solely for displaying these metrics on your watch face. This information is processed locally on your device and is not shared with us or any third parties.
Data Sharing and Disclosure
No Data Sharing:
Since we do not collect any data, there is no data to share or disclose to third parties.
Security
The application is designed to utilize only the necessary information from your device to provide the functionality of the watch face. No personal information is transmitted outside of your device, ensuring that your data remains private and secure.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
master80090@gmail.com
Conclusion
By using the Watch Face Application, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. We are committed to providing a safe and secure experience for our users, and your privacy is our priority.